g><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104hpa1714482903383.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hpa1714482903383.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/hpa1714482903383.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qwl1665702783474\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $split\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"qwl1665702783474___split_290094\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Split a string.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"qwl1665702783474__topic_d89591e1_d89592e1_d89593e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qwl1665702783474__p_d89594e1_d89595e1_d89596e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Return</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$split</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Source</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">StartPos</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">SearchFor</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LeftPart</var> {<code class=\"ph codeph\">,</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">RightPart</var>}}<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"qwl1665702783474__section_w4138ab1b7b5_w4139ab1b7_w4140ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qwl1665702783474__p_d89597e1_d89598e1_d89599e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">vStatus = $split(vFieldname, 1, \".\",vField, vEntity)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qwl1665702783474__topic_d59602e1_d59603e1_d59604e1_d59605e1_d59606e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d489265e116\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"4\" id=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Parameter</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Data Type</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Direction</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Source</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">String</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">In</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">String that needs to be split.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">StartPos</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Numeric</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">In</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">Position in <var class=\"keyword varname\">Source</var> where the search needs to start.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">SearchFor</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">String</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">In</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">Substring to find; can be a constant string, regex string, or syntax\n                           string.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">LeftPart</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">String</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Out</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">String to the left of the split.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">RightPart</var>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">String</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Out</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qwl1665702783474__table_d9692e1_d9693e1_d9694e1__entry__4\">\n<p class=\"p\">String to the right of the split.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qwl1665702783474__topic_d59607e1_d59608e1_d59609e1_d59610e1_d59611e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d489265e326\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qwl1665702783474__d5916e20\">Allowed in all component types.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qwl1665702783474__topic_d59612e1_d59613e1_d59614e1_d59615e1_d59616e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d489265e336\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qwl1665702783474__p_d89612e1_d89613e1_d89614e1\">Position of the <var class=\"keyword varname\">SearchFor</var> substring within the string.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qwl1665702783474__p_d89615e1_d89616e1_d89617e1\">If the <var class=\"keyword varname\">SearchFor</var> substring is not found, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$split</span> returns <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> in <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$status</span> and the Out parameters <var class=\"keyword varname\">LeftPart</var> and <var class=\"keyword varname\">RightPart</var> are empty.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qwl1665702783474__section_kwj_1x3_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d489265e370\">Example: $split </h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">In the following example, a field name that includes the entity name\n               is split into the field and entity parts by the dot.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"qwl1665702783474__pre_ahy_1x3_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">variables\n string vFieldname\n string vField, vEntity\n numeric vStatus\nendVariables\nvFieldname = \"Field.Entity\"\nvStatus = $split(vFieldname, 1, \".\",vField, vEntity)\n; vStatus = 6\n; vField = \"Field\"\n; vEntity = \"entity\"\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n<p class=\"p\">In the following example, a string is split into parts by the colon, dot, or\n               semicolon.</p>\n<div class=\"zDocsCodeExplanationContainer\"><button aria-label=\"Explain this code\" class=\"zDocsAiActionsButton\" data-target=\"#zDocsCodeExplanationModal_uniface_104hpa1714482903383_html_0\" data-toggle=\"modal\" tabindex=\"0\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-code-explanation\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-code-explanation\"></use></svg>Explain this code</button></div><div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre codeblock language-plaintext\" data-explanation-rendered=\"true\" id=\"qwl1665702783474__codeblock_xvm_w32_gbc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">variables  \n string vText, vPre\n numeric vStatus \nendVariables\nvStatus = -1\nvText = \"Uniface:Field.Entity;Good\"\nwhile(vStatus != 0)   \n vStatus = $split(vText,1,$regex(\"[:|.|;]\"),vPre, vText) \nendwhile\n; First loop: vPre is \"Uniface\", vText is \"Field.Entity;Good\", vStatus is 8.\n; Second loop: vPre is \" Field \", vText is \"Entity;Good\", vStatus is 6.\n; Third loop: vPre is \" Entity \", vText is \"Good\", vStatus is 7.\n; Fourth loop: vPre is NULL, vText is NULL, vStatus is 0.</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6811623\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_6811623\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$split Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $split Split a string. Return = $split ( Source , StartPos , SearchFor { , LeftPart { , RightPart }} ) Example: vStatus = $split(vFieldname, 1, \".\",vField, vEntity) Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Direction Description Source String In String that needs to be split. StartPos Numeric In Position in Source where the search needs to start. SearchFor String In Substring to find; can be a constant string, regex string, or syntax string. LeftPart String Out String to the left of the split. RightPart String Out String to the right of the split. Use Allowed in all component types. Return Values Position of the SearchFor substring within the string. If the SearchFor substring is not found, $split returns 0 in $status and the Out parameters LeftPart and RightPart are empty. Example: $split In the following example, a field name that includes the entity name is split into the field and entity parts by the dot. variables string vFieldname string vField, vEntity numeric vStatus endVariables vFieldname = \"Field.Entity\" vStatus = $split(vFieldname, 1, \".\",vField, vEntity) ; vStatus = 6 ; vField = \"Field\" ; vEntity = \"entity\" Copy In the following example, a string is split into parts by the colon, dot, or semicolon. Explain this code variables string vText, vPre numeric vStatus endVariables vStatus = -1 vText = \"Uniface:Field.Entity;Good\" while(vStatus != 0) vStatus = $split(vText,1,$regex(\"[:|.|;]\"),vPre, vText) endwhile ; First loop: vPre is \"Uniface\", vText is \"Field.Entity;Good\", vStatus is 8. ; Second loop: vPre is \" Field \", vText is \"Entity;Good\", vStatus is 6. ; Third loop: vPre is \" Entity \", vText is \"Good\", vStatus is 7. ; Fourth loop: vPre is NULL, vText is NULL, vStatus is 0. Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}